DateTime::Locale::rw_RW(3) User Contributed Perl Documentation DateTime::Locale::rw_RW(3)

NAME

DateTime::Locale::rw_RW - Locale data examples for the Kinyarwanda Rwanda (rw-RW) locale

DESCRIPTION

This pod file contains examples of the locale data available for the Kinyarwanda Rwanda locale.

  Kuwa mbere
  Kuwa kabiri
  Kuwa gatatu
  Kuwa kane
  Kuwa gatanu
  Kuwa gatandatu
  Ku cyumweru

  mbe.
  kab.
  gtu.
  kan.
  gnu.
  gnd.
  cyu.

Date Formats

Full

   2008-02-05T18:30:30 = 2008 Gashyantare 5, Kuwa kabiri
   1995-12-22T09:05:02 = 1995 Ukuboza 22, Kuwa gatanu
  -0010-09-15T04:44:23 = -10 Nzeli 15, Kuwa gatandatu

Long

   2008-02-05T18:30:30 = 2008 Gashyantare 5
   1995-12-22T09:05:02 = 1995 Ukuboza 22
  -0010-09-15T04:44:23 = -10 Nzeli 15

Medium

   2008-02-05T18:30:30 = 2008 gas. 5
   1995-12-22T09:05:02 = 1995 uku. 22
  -0010-09-15T04:44:23 = -10 nze. 15

Short

   2008-02-05T18:30:30 = 2008-02-05
   1995-12-22T09:05:02 = 1995-12-22
  -0010-09-15T04:44:23 = -10-09-15

Available Formats

   1995-12-22T09:05:02 = 9 B
  -0010-09-15T04:44:23 = 4 B
